             were indicted, for <rs id="t18100718-16-off85" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18100718-16-off85" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100718-16-off85" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18100718-16-victim182" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
                           Sibbald
                        <interp inst="t18100718-16-victim182" type="surname" value="Sibbald"></interp>
